# Evaluation fixture skeleton

Use only synthetic and anonymized samples. Do not add real resumes, real JDs, or any PII.

Required fixture set:
- `resumes/tech_en`
- `resumes/non_tech` (one non-tech domain sample)
- `resumes/tricky_two_column`
- `resumes/de_resume`
- `jds/clean_en`
- `jds/messy_multi_role_en`
- `jds/de_jd`
